The country of Yemen is unapparelled to any other place on this Earth. From its breathtaking scenery to its history that dates back to the beginning of man. Yemen is the homeland of our family. As first-generation immigrants, we wanted to honor our heritage. Yemen is where coffee was invented and later flourished in global trade. Roasting and serving coffee is something that is inclusive of all people and cultures, and brings people together. Our coffee is grown from altitudes over 3,000 ft in a mountainous village called Haraz, where our namesake originates.

reviews_data.review_text: Great coffee, amazing ambiance and friendly staff.

Obsessed with this cafe!
Honestly, their drinks are always on point.. especially the caramel frappe, it’s my absolute favorite! 😍 And don’t get me started on their baked goods… ever since they opened the new branch, everything tastes so fresh. I literally can’t walk out without grabbing their bee bites 🤤 they’re just too good to resist! Also, major shoutout for being one of the few cafes that stays open late. That alone has saved me more times than I can count. Late night cravings? Sorted. I genuinely recommend this place.. it’s totally worth it!
Best coffee shop ever! The staff is super friendly, and the new place is spacious with a great atmosphere. Their drinks are amazing too. It was such a great experience!

reviews_data.review_text: The drinks were refreshingly cold, however, the team's performance could have been more professional.  The space was clean, though.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Omar! Thank you for stopping by Haraz Coffee House. We appreciate your diligent review and honesty. We always strive to provide the best customer service to all of our guests and ensure they all leave our shop pleased and satisfied. Please reach out to management to let us know what transpired during your visit and we will do everything we can to help. 

Please reach out to us at 313-300-8044 for any questions you may have. 

Thank you,
Haraz Management

reviews_data.review_text: The coffee was made with art hand ☕️🔥

First time at this location. Spendy spot, but delightful coffee and treats. We tried their traditional coffee, wife liked it. Also Dubai chocolate cookie, slice of tiramisu, and a latte.

Everything was quite nice.

Very clean, feels very new here. Welcoming, too.

Bummer they didn't have the Dubai chocolate croissant here, that thing is so so so good.

Snagged a Dubai chocolate bar for later. Hopefully it slaps too, $8 for a fairly small bar.

Absolutely love this place! Haraz Coffee is one of the best coffee shops in town. The pistachio latte and pistachio milk cake are so delicious! The ambiance is warm and inviting, with beautiful decor. Highly recommend!
Love the new location! Very spacious and a great place to study or meet up with friends. All their coffee is amazing, but I love the pistachio latte!
Spacious, friendly staff, & unique high end coffee options
Best coffe shop in town
Came in for a Latte which was exceptionally made.
Best coffee around and great service. Haraz is awesome!

review_questions.Seating type: Indoor dining area, Private dining room

reviews_data.review_text: Amazing coffee and tea shop! Excellent addition to the Loso neighborhood and service was amazing.
Amazing. Owner very personable. Outstanding service.
My favorite coffee shop opening soon 🙏
